"{\"uid\": \"binnews.com-content-2024-01-10-simone-biles-says-she-felt-like-failure-following-tokyo-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Photo:Getty Images  Simone Bilesis opening up about feeling like a \\\"failure\\\" after the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles made the confession in a interview for the cover for the cover of February'sVanity Fair.\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The star gymnast said her experience with the \\\"twisties\\\" and other mental health issues during the Tokyo Olympics was a low moment in her life.\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish I could sit here and tell you it was glorious,\\\" Biles said of hertwo-year hiatus from international competition.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I took a break after 2016, I had the time of my life.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was doing anything and everything.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But after 2020, it was kind of depressing until I started therapy and got help.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like a failure.\\\"\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even though I was empowering so many people and speaking out about mental health, every time I talked about my experience in Tokyo - because it obviously did not go the way that I had planned - it stung a little bit,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But all in all, it was the best decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Biles said she did not like how the public put her on a \\\"pedestal as a mental-health advocate.\\\"\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was not okay with that,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can be a lending hand and help people, then I will be open, honest, and vulnerable, but you cannot stick me in front of a crowd and say, 'Do everything she's doing.'\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"  Since pulling out of the Tokyo Olympics, Biles said she has overcome her fear and is ready for the 2024 Summer Olympics if she's called on.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I do not make it to Paris, it will not absolutely crush me,\\\" Biles told Vanity Fair.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997087875696, \"rank\": 2.912125612157675e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanity_Fair_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.9083471797489278, \"rank\": 0.09190153882040974, \"text\": \"Vanity Fair\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanity_Fair_(magazine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanity_Fair_(magazine)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Black Information Network is your source for Black News!\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Information_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Black Information Network\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Information_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Information_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9040996163464794, \"rank\": 0.10607131024506826, \"text\": 